snippet.title: Dykom Software - Dev Vlog 3
snippet.description:
In this unexpected and 3rd installment of the game dev vlog Mike desperately tries to catch up on 3 years worth of news and updates for Arksync, while simultaneously trying to win back the trust and hearts of his own audience.

SUBSCRIBE TO THE CHANNEL... or else.

WISHLIST ON STEAM... or else.
